luatransform

Copyright (C) 2012 Dimitris Papavasileiou <dpapavas@gmail.com>

luatransform is a module which provides linear algebra operations to
Lua such as generation of rotation, reflection, projection and shear
matrices, concatenation of transforms and application to vectors as
well as elementary matrix and vector operations.

It is mainly targeted towards use for computer graphics applications
and is built on top of luaarray which provides efficient
imlplementatation of vector and matrix-like structures for Lua.
